  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: "Niyabetin Devri \u2013 Rubens"
  description: "Peter Paul Rubens, Niyabetin Devri (La Remise de la R\xE9gence),
    1622\u201325. Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya. Galerie M\xE9dicis, Louvre.
    Marie de' Medici Serisi'nden olan bu tabloda IV. Henri, Almanya seferine \xE7\u0131kmadan
    \xF6nce kar\u0131s\u0131 Marie de' Medici'ye d\xFCnyay\u0131 simgeleyen k\xFCreyi
    (globus cruciger) teslim ederek krall\u0131\u011F\u0131n y\xF6netimini ona devreder;
    aralar\u0131ndaki k\xFC\xE7\xFCk fig\xFCr ise veliaht prens (gelece\u011Fin XIII.
    Louis'i) olarak hanedan\u0131n devam"
