  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 94c46ecd48d7cdb4786744f4644a0188, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: "Angoul\xEAme M\xFCzakereleri \u2013 Rubens"
  description: "Peter Paul Rubens, Angoul\xEAme M\xFCzakereleri (Les N\xE9gociations
    d'Angoul\xEAme), 1622\u201325. Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya. Galerie
    M\xE9dicis, Louvre. Marie de' Medici Serisi'nden olan bu tabloda 1619'da XIII.
    Louis taraf\u0131ndan g\xF6nderilen Kardinal de La Rochefoucauld'nun, s\xFCrg\xFCndeki
    Krali\xE7e ile o\u011Flu aras\u0131ndaki bar\u0131\u015F\u0131 sa\u011Flamak
    \xFCzere y\xFCr\xFCtt\xFC\u011F\xFC m\xFCzakereler resmedilir. Sa\u011Fdaki kanatl\u0131
    fig\xFCr ise tanr\u0131lar\u0131n habercisi Merk\xFCr'd\xFCr; diplomasi ve uzla\u015Fma
    s\xFCrecini simgeleyerek el\xE7inin kutsal g\xF6revini y\xFCceltir."
