  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: "IV. Henri'nin Tanr\u0131la\u015Ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131 ve Naipli\u011Fin
    \u0130lan\u0131 \u2013 Rubens"
  description: "Peter Paul Rubens, IV. Henri'nin Tanr\u0131la\u015Ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131
    ve Naipli\u011Fin \u0130lan\u0131, 1622\u201325. Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya.
    Galerie M\xE9dicis, Louvre. Marie de' Medici Serisi'nin merkezindeki en \xF6nemli
    tablodur. Solda, 14 May\u0131s 1610'da Ravaillac taraf\u0131ndan suikaste kurban
    giden IV. Henri, J\xFCpiter ve Saturn taraf\u0131ndan g\xF6\u011Fe \xE7\u0131kar\u0131larak
    tanr\u0131la\u015Ft\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r; sa\u011Fda ise Marie de' Medici, Fransa
    ve di\u011Fer alegorik fig\xFCrler taraf\u0131ndan o\u011Flu ad\u0131na naip
    ilan edilirken yas tutar."
