  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 94c46ecd48d7cdb4786744f4644a0188, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: "Marie de' Medici Portresi \u2013 Frans Pourbus"
  description: "Frans Pourbus le Jeune (Gen\xE7), Marie de' Medici Portresi, yakla\u015F\u0131k
    1610. Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya. Louvre M\xFCzesi. Galerie M\xE9dicis'in
    giri\u015Finde yer alan bu g\xF6rkemli resmi t\xF6ren portresinde Krali\xE7e,
    a\u011F\u0131r i\u015Flemeli siyah saten gelinli\u011Fi, geni\u015F dantelli
    yakas\u0131 ve m\xFCcevherleriyle Fransa Krali\xE7esi'nin t\xFCm ha\u015Fmetiyle
    resmedilir. Pourbus, d\xF6neminin en \xF6nemli saray portrecilerinden biri olarak
    Avrupa hanedanlar\u0131n\u0131n resmi k\u0131yafetlerini ve hiyerar\u015Fik duru\u015Funu
    en ince detay\u0131na kadar yans\u0131tmas\u0131yla \xFCnl\xFCd\xFCr."
