  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: "Niyabet H\xFCk\xFCmeti \u2013 Rubens"
  description: "Peter Paul Rubens, Niyabet H\xFCk\xFCmeti (Le Gouvernement de la
    Reine), 1622\u201325. Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya. Galerie M\xE9dicis,
    Louvre. Marie de' Medici Serisi'nden olan bu alegorik tabloda Krali\xE7e, taht\u0131nda
    y\xFCkseltilmi\u015F olarak resmedilirken Bilgelik, Adalet, Bereket ve Sadakat
    gibi erdemleri temsil eden allegorik fig\xFCrler etraf\u0131nda toplan\u0131r;
    a\u015Fa\u011F\u0131daki uzanan nehir tanr\u0131s\u0131 fig\xFCr\xFC Fransa'n\u0131n
    topraklar\u0131n\u0131 ve refah\u0131n\u0131 simgeleyerek Krali\xE7e'nin naipli\u011Fi
    d\xF6neminde \xFClkeye getirdi\u011Fi iyi y\xF6netimi y\xFCceltir."
