  description: "Peter Paul Rubens, Marie de' Medici'nin E\u011Fitimi, 1622\u201325.
    Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya. Galerie M\xE9dicis, Louvre. Marie de' Medici
    Serisi'nden olan bu tabloda gen\xE7 prensesin Minerva, Apollon ve \xDC\xE7 G\xFCzeller
    taraf\u0131ndan sanat ve bilimler konusunda e\u011Fitildi\u011Fi alegorik bir
    sahne canland\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r."
