  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: "Marie de' Medici'nin Kaderi (\xDC\xE7 Kader Tanr\u0131\xE7as\u0131)
    \u2013 Rubens"
  description: "Peter Paul Rubens, Marie de' Medici'nin Kaderi / \xDC\xE7 Kader Tanr\u0131\xE7as\u0131
    (Le Destin de Marie de M\xE9dicis), 1622\u201325. Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya.
    Galerie M\xE9dicis, Louvre. Marie de' Medici Serisi'nin a\xE7\u0131l\u0131\u015F
    tablosudur. En \xFCstte sarma\u015F dola\u015F resmedilen J\xFCpiter ile Juno,
    Krali\xE7e'nin do\u011Fumunu kutsarken; ortada Yunan mitolojisinin \xFC\xE7 Kader
    Tanr\u0131\xE7as\u0131 (Klotho, Lakhesis ve Atropos) Marie'nin hayat ipli\u011Fini
    e\u011Firir, \xF6l\xE7er ve keser. Bu tablo, Krali\xE7e'nin tanr\u0131lar taraf\u0131ndan
    \xF6nceden belirlenmi\u015F \u015Fanl\u0131 kaderini ilan ederek t\xFCm serinin
    alegorik \xE7er\xE7evesini kurar."
