  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: "Tanr\u0131lar Meclisi \u2013 Rubens"
  description: "Peter Paul Rubens, Tanr\u0131lar Meclisi (Le Conseil des Dieux),
    1622\u201325. Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya. Galerie M\xE9dicis, Louvre.
    Marie de' Medici Serisi'nden olan bu alegorik tabloda Olimpos tanr\u0131lar\u0131
    J\xFCpiter ve Juno ba\u015Fkanl\u0131\u011F\u0131nda toplan\u0131r; Frans\u0131z-\u0130spanyol
    hanedanlar\u0131 aras\u0131ndaki \xE7ifte evlilik anla\u015Fmas\u0131n\u0131
    (Marie'nin \xE7ocuklar\u0131n\u0131n \u0130spanya kraliyet ailesiyle evlenmesi)
    tart\u0131\u015F\u0131p onaylarken Apollon, Nifak y\u0131lan\u0131n\u0131 oklar\u0131yla
    def ederek bu birli\u011Fin kutsall\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131 simgeler."
