  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: "Niyabet Saltanat\u0131n\u0131n Mutlulu\u011Fu \u2013 Rubens"
  description: "Peter Paul Rubens, Niyabet Saltanat\u0131n\u0131n Mutlulu\u011Fu
    (Le Bonheur de la R\xE9gence), 1622\u201325. Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya.
    Galerie M\xE9dicis, Louvre. Marie de' Medici Serisi'nden olan bu alegorik tabloda
    Krali\xE7e, Adalet terazisini tutan Astraea olarak aslanlar\u0131n \xE7ekti\u011Fi
    zafer arabas\u0131nda resmedilir; yukar\u0131da bulutlar\u0131n aras\u0131nda
    tanr\u0131lar ve g\xF6kku\u015Fa\u011F\u0131, onun naipli\u011Fi d\xF6neminde
    Fransa'ya getirdi\u011Fi bar\u0131\u015F, bolluk ve refah\u0131 simgeler."
