  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: "Louis XIII'\xFCn Do\u011Fumu \u2013 Rubens"
  description: "Peter Paul Rubens, Louis XIII'\xFCn Do\u011Fumu (Fontainebleau'da),
    1622\u201325. Tuval \xFCzerine ya\u011Fl\u0131boya. Galerie M\xE9dicis, Louvre.
    Marie de' Medici Serisi'nden olan bu tabloda 27 Eyl\xFCl 1601'de Fontainebleau
    Saray\u0131'nda do\u011Fan veliaht prens, sonradan Kral XIII. Louis'in d\xFCnyaya
    geli\u015Fi resmedilir; Krali\xE7e yeni do\u011Fan o\u011Flunu kuca\u011F\u0131nda
    tutarken Sa\u011Fl\u0131k, Bereket ve sadakati simgeleyen k\xF6pek fig\xFCr\xFCyle
    birlikte alegorik tanr\u0131lar bu kutsal an\u0131 kutlar."
